  <brief_title>Video-Based Delivery of HIV Test Information for Spanish-Speaking Latinos</brief_title>
  <official_title>Video-Based Delivery of HIV Test Information for Spanish-Speaking Latinos</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Rhode Island Hospital</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Rhode Island Hospital</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to determine if a Spanish-language HIV and HIV test information
      video is as effective in delivering basic information regarding HIV and HIV tests to
      primarily Spanish-speaking HIV test recipients as an in-person presentation with an HIV test
      counselor.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
